---- MODULE ParticipantVoiceStatePlusCal ----
\* Voice state machine for a single room participant. Tracks microphone and listening status.
\* PlusCal version — generated by tlaiser
\* https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

CONSTANTS Connected, Muted, Deafened, Priority

